data.description: Walk in to this beautiful southwest style 4 bedroom 3 bath home with a spacious 3 car garage. The primary bedroom is on the main floor with a HUGE family room, spacious kitchen with lots of cabinet space and kitchen island, Upstairs has 3 large bedrooms and walk-way that leads to an additional living area with a balcony that overlooks the beautiful backyard. with views. Backyard access available with RV or boat parking. Plus owned solar on the home will make for very low electric bills. Come and make this one your home before its gone!
